<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77eb320c-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s460vv–15"><num value="460vv–15">§ 460vv–15.</num><heading> Grazing</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Subject to such limitations, conditions, or regulations as he may prescribe, the Secretary of Agriculture shall permit grazing on lands within the Ouachita National Forest, Le Flore County, Oklahoma.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id77eb320d-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/100/499/s17">Pub. L. 100–499, § 17</ref>, <date date="1988-10-18">Oct. 18, 1988</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/102/2499">102 Stat. 2499</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
